title: No. 23 Cal prepares for high altitude at No. 5 Utah
text:
Photo: Michael Macor / The Chronicle Cal head coach Sonny Dykes keeps watch late in the game, as the California Bears went on to beat the Washington State Cougars34-28 at Memorial Stadium in Berkeley, Calif., on Sat. October 3, 2015. Cal head coach Sonny Dykes keeps watch late in the game, as the...
Sonny Dykes lived in Lubbock, Texas, for about two decades without thinking much about elevation. Then this week, while researching Salt Lake City, the Cal head coach learned that his hometown sits 3,212 feet above sea level.
